Class Content

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn2.ecommerce.product.Content
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContentWithSize

    public abstract class Content
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class represents content objects and encapsulates all the properties of a content which are common to Application, Wallpaper and Ringtone
